	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Your towering intellect has provided you with a deep well of preparedness - and an assistant. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Constitution, or Intelligence increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>Your Exertion pool increases by 1.</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.jet01i63abb2v66h]{Measure Twice, Cut Once} can now provide common magic items. You must still abide by the usual gold piece restrictions.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die with a skill you are proficient with. The maximum expertise die for the chosen skill becomes a d12.</p></li><li><p>Choose one of the following follower types: Apothecary, Cook, Diviner, Healer, Minstrel, or Sage. You gain the capabilities of an Expert follower of the chosen type.</p></li></ul><p>Once you have selected this feat, you can no longer gain levels in classes other than Scholar.</p>",
